# InvestAI — SEBI Investment Adviser

## Local Chalane Ke Liye
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
GROQ_API_KEY=your_key streamlit run app.py
```

## Render Par Deploy Karne Ke Liye
1. GitHub par push karo
2. Render.com par naya Web Service banao
3. Environment variable mein GROQ_API_KEY add karo
4. Deploy karo!

